column108: Spectacular lakefront home w/awesome views & deep water dock on Lake Thurmond! Copper roof, stone exterior, walnut floors, exquisite moldings & finish, fabulous rec room, exercise studio, study & guest cottage. 7318 sf main house, 640 sf guest cottage & 3218 sf decks & covered porches for indoor/outdoor living at it finest! 4+ garages for all your toys. Designed by Wm T. Baker, built by Rob Marett
